FT  30 JUN 92 / World News In Brief: Rangers cleared of Ward murder
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Two Kenyan park rangers were cleared by Nairobi's Supreme Court of murdering
British tourist Julie Ward, 28, whose mutilated remains were found in the
bush nearly four years ago.
