<TEXT>
Mosaic Investments is to sell the bulk of its engineering and automotive
division for Pounds 10.4m cash in a management buy out.
The management team, comprising certain Mosaic subsidiary directors, is
supported by equity funding arranged by Midland Montagu Ventures and
co-underwritten by County NatWest Ventures.
