Gerhard Kurz, president of Mobil Shipping and Transportation, has been
elected chairman of the executive committee of the OIL COMPANIES
INTERNATIONAL MARINE FORUM.
*****
David Hughff has been appointed a director of SMITH &amp; PINCHING.
