<HEADLINE>
FT  29 JUN 92 / World News in Brief: White sheet protest
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Thousands of people on the Italian island of Sardinia hung bedsheets from
windows to protest against the kidnap five months ago of eight-year-old
Farouk Kassam. The kidnappers recently sent Farouk's family part of one of
the boy's ears and demanded L7bn (Pounds 3.2m) ransom.
</TEXT>
