FT  27 JUN 92 / Economic Diary
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
MONDAY: Major British banking groups' quarterly analysis of lending (March -
May). London sterling certificates of deposit (May). Monetary statistics
(including bank and building society balance sheets (May). Bill turnover
statistics (May). Sterling commercial paper (May). Money market statistics
