Industrial and commercial companies (first quarter). US leading indicators
(May). Interim results from Lonrho.
WEDNESDAY: Overseas travel and tourism (April). Advance energy statistics
(May). US NAPM (June); construction spending (May). United Kingdom takes
over the European Community presidency (until December 31). Italy takes over
